# Polymarket Safety

- MVP scope is paper trading and replay only.
- Do not add live order placement unless the user explicitly requests a separate live-trading phase.
- Do not implement or suggest geoblock bypassing.
- Verify Polymarket access, CLOB V2 behavior, fees, and API shapes against official docs or read-only endpoints before relying on assumptions.
- Keep BTC, ETH, and SOL as the only default assets unless the user expands scope.
- Do not add wallet/private-key handling, signing, or order-routing code to the hot path without a separate live-readiness design and approval.
